## [0.0.2] - 2025-01-21

### Added
- multiple example corpuses added
- run_evaluation.py, responsible for calcualting the F1 Score, Precision, Recall, Accuracy

### Changed
- hipe_loader.py adapted to normalize datasets, using MASTER_TAG_MAP and standardize_tag function
- tokenize_and_alligne.py changed to work with dynamical feature selection
- tokenize_and_alligne.py changed to work with with only test datasets as well (dynamical selection of "test" set if exists)
- run_training.py adapted to run training on multiple datasets

## [0.0.1] - 2025-01-19

### Added
- corpus_inference added with sample corpus

### Changed
- Weighting changed to Inverse Document Frequency
- Loss function changed to Weighted Categorical Cross-Entropy Loss
- Cleanup in each file
- README.md updated

## [0.0.0] - 2025-12-17

### Added
- Initial implementation of teh NER pipeline